### Canonical enum values (authoritative — never use alternatives)

- **Inventory status:** `Draft`, `In stock`, `Listed`, `Sold`, `Reserved`, `Retired` (ADR-002, ADR-017)
- **Condition code:** `Mint/Near Mint`, `Excellent`, `Very Good`, `Good`, `Fair/As-Is` (ADR-002, ADR-017)
- **Order status:** `active`, `void`, `cancelled` (ADR-017)
- **Payment status:** `unpaid`, `paid`, `refunded` (ADR-017, ADR-039)
- **Customer note type:** `general`, `shipping_preference`, `communication`, `follow_up`, `complaint` (ADR-065)
- **Activity log source:** `user`, `system`, `etsy_sync` (ADR-037)
- **Listing draft state:** `draft`, `generated`, `imported`, `approved`, `published`
- **Listing draft source:** `manual`, `integrated_ai`, `portable_import`
- **Etsy who_made:** `i_did`, `someone_else`, `collective` (ADR-017 §1b; default `someone_else` for vintage)
- **Etsy when_made:** `made_to_order`, `2020_2026`, `2010_2019`, `2004_2009`, `2000_2003`, `1990s`, `1980s`, `1970s`, `1960s`, `1950s`, `1940s`, `1930s`, `1920s`, `1910s`, `1900s`, `1800s`, `1700s`, `before_1700` (ADR-017 §1a)
- **Weight unit:** `oz`, `lb`, `g`, `kg` (ADR-017)
- **Dimensions unit:** `in`, `ft`, `mm`, `cm`, `m` (ADR-017)
- **Photo shot type:** `hero`, `angle`, `detail`, `backstamp`, `scale`, `imperfection`, `underside`, `grouping`, `lifestyle`, `measurement`, `extra` (ADR-072 §Photo classification)
- **Source channel:** `etsy`, `manual`
- **Shipper:** `USPS`, `UPS`, `FedEx`, `DHL`, `Other` (ADR-004)

